# 🚨 Root Cause (confirmed)

Your subscriptions are **mixed between catalogs**:

| Operator     | Source  | Problem |
| ------------ | ------- | ------- |
| odf-operator | ✅ v4.20 | OK      |
| ALL others   | ❌ v4.19 | WRONG   |

Example:

```text
cephcsi-operator → cs-redhat-operator-index-v4-19 ❌
mcg-operator     → cs-redhat-operator-index-v4-19 ❌
