# 🚀 Option 2 (quick patch – faster)

Patch all subscriptions:

```bash
for i in $(oc get sub -n openshift-storage -o name | grep -v odf-operator); do
  oc patch $i -n openshift-storage \
  --type=merge \
  -p '{"spec":{"source":"cs-redhat-operator-index-v4-20"}}'
done
```

